Description: NO CASE. This guitar does NOT come with a case. Get a Zakk Wylde autographed guitar! Auction is for the buzzsaw guitar shown. Over ten years of wall hanging or in case and ready for new home. Barely played before zakk signing (staples center, nov 30 2007) and not after except for me to check controls for this listing! Check the reflections of my windows and blinds in the clear coat in these pics. Hard to find anything wrong with this guitar to tell you about. I will direct your attention to the side neck pic where you can see a bit of an uneven edge where the clear coat meets the white neck binding in some spots, something present from the factory and something also on two other Wylde epiphone les Pauls I have straight from guitar center and musicians friend but something I wanted to point out for you. Towards the edge of the autograph you see in one pic maybe a bit of the autograph line is lighter probably due to a past cleaning that was too quick. Awesome guitar with very little time on it at all; a wall hanger. shipping/handling to lower 48 states only! I’m just an individual not guitar center so shipping cost is very high for me on guitars, sorry but I don’t get a special deal with ups and have eaten as high as around 130 to ship a guitar so if you cannot handle shipping/handling cost please don’t bid.
Title: 2005 Epiphone Zakk Wylde Custom Les Paul Autographed Electric Guitar NO CASE
